Stephanie's passion for bridges led her to initially consider a career as a bridge builder. Whilst she has secretly still not given up on this goal, Stephanie became Head of Studio at Wooga in the meantime. Wooga is one of the most popular game developers for web and mobile in the world.

Stephanie designed the Facebook title Monster World, and developed a method of strictly metrics-driven design and weekly iterations. Being live for more than three years now her team has managed to keep Monster World an enjoyable game on Facebook and iOS until today and one of Woogas' most successful titles.

While Stephanie still cares a lot about her monsters, she is now responsible for one of Woogas' game studios.

